{"items":[{"id":"67209","user":{"id":"203577","nickname":"技术喵","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/FjdGLKY8l4RINPdZ02073fwKFxPK","subject_id":228,"work_shop_name":"编程猫官方","work_shop_level":4,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":2,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p>喵~在源码世界里，角色面向移动的方向：</p>\n<p><font color=\"#ff0000\">0度为右边，90度为上边，180度为左边，270度为下边</font></p>\n<p>比如“编程猫向右走”这个角色，本身就是图像上就是<font color=\"#ff0000\">面向右边</font>，那么我们只要设置按下左箭头，向左移动10步，就要面向180度，向右就是面向0度，移动10步。<img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FkBVyO8aOYbhA9l2aWxBs1cCyhqS\"></p>\n<p>那如果是“火球球”这个角色，图像显示是面向的左边，但是实际这个角色的面向角度还是0的哦，也就是与角色实际面向的方向，与角色显示的图像方向是相反的<img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FrfmxBaz4J7o1_57Zm9tm7KZ8N9G\"></p>\n<p>那么我们就要设置角色向面向的反方向移动，也就是移动-10步。</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://img.t.sinajs.cn/t4/appstyle/expression/ext/normal/a5/hb_fahongbao2016_thumb.gif\"><br></p>\n<p>遇到Bug记得呼叫技术喵QQ：2950389506</p>\n<p><br></p>","n_comments":1,"updated_at":1518158984,"created_at":1518158984,"earliest_comments":[{"id":"1849691","user":{"id":"11806884","nickname":"林夕狐","avatar_url":"https://cdn-community.codemao.cn/47/community/d2ViXzEwMDFfMTE4MDY4ODRfMTE4MDY4ODRfMTY3MzMxNTczMDE5OV85MGQwODAyNg.jpeg","subject_id":17972,"work_shop_name":"幻狐工作室","work_shop_level":1,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"捉技术猫）））","created_at":1675600081}]},{"id":"1520177","user":{"id":"10295601","nickname":"阿白kCMT","avatar_url":"https://static-platform.codemao.cn/production/avatar/custom/17e97dcf-2b64-47eb-a916-742275c722bf","subject_id":16083,"work_shop_name":"ETO","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"is_top":false,"n_likes":0,"is_liked":false,"content":"<p><img style=\"max-width: 100%; display: block; margin: 0 auto;\" src=\"https://cdn-community.codemao.cn/47/community/d2ViXzMwMDFfMTAyOTU2MDFfOTI2NF8xNjc1NjAxMjAxMTUzXzdhYTgyZWFj.gif\" alt=\"center_image\"></p>","n_comments":0,"updated_at":1675601202,"created_at":1675601202,"earliest_comments":[]},